            <history-note id="DLM180827"><amended-provision>Section 105(8)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>substituted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>17 May 2006</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM372922">section 15(3)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Education Amendment Act 2006</amending-leg> (2006 No 19).</history-note>
            <history-note id="DLM180828"><amended-provision>Section 105(9)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>added</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>17 May 2006</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM372922">section 15(3)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Education Amendment Act 2006</amending-leg> (2006 No 19).</history-note>
            <history-note id="DLM1885427"><amended-provision>Section 105(10)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>added</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>17 May 2006</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM372922">section 15(3)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Education Amendment Act 2006</amending-leg> (2006 No 19).</history-note>
