            <history-note id="DLM181161"><amended-provision>Section 122(d)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>substituted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 January 1997</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM403263">section 3(3)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Education Amendment Act 1996</amending-leg> (1996 No 98).</history-note>
