            <history-note id="DLM181170"><amended-provision>Section 124(1)(e)(ii)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>23 July 1990</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM212648">section 25</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Education Amendment Act 1990</amending-leg> (1990 No 60).</history-note>
