            <history-note id="DLM181173"><amended-provision>Section 124(3)(b)(ii)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 February 2002</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM118874">section 82(2)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Education Standards Act 2001</amending-leg> (2001 No 88).</history-note>
            <history-note id="DLM181171"><amended-provision>Section 124(4)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>repealed</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>25 June 1993</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM302600">section 10(3)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Education Amendment Act 1993</amending-leg> (1993 No 51).</history-note>
