            <history-note id="DLM1886731"><amended-provision>Section 135A</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 February 2002</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM118874">section 82(2)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Education Standards Act 2001</amending-leg> (2001 No 88).</history-note>
