            <history-note id="DLM1759241"><amended-provision>Section 144A(1)(b)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>substituted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 December 2008</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM373075">section 57</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Education Amendment Act 2006</amending-leg> (2006 No 19).</history-note>
            <history-note id="DLM182052"><amended-provision>Section 144A(1A)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>inserted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>25 October 2001</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM118437">section 38(3)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Education Standards Act 2001</amending-leg> (2001 No 88).</history-note>
