            <history-note id="DLM1150813"><amended-provision>Section 159F(1)(d)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>substituted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 January 2008</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM1062834">section 14(4)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Education (Tertiary Reforms) Amendment Act 2007</amending-leg> (2007 No 106).</history-note>
