            <history-note id="DLM183196"><amended-provision>Section 159J(6)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>substituted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>25 January 2005</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM331111">section 200</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Crown Entities Act 2004</amending-leg> (2004 No 115).</history-note>
