            <history-note id="DLM185161"><amended-provision>Section 228(2A)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>inserted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 January 1992</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM253139">section 25(1)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Education Amendment Act (No 4) 1991</amending-leg> (1991 No 136).</history-note>
