            <history-note id="DLM1891920"><amended-provision>Section 253(1)(f)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>25 October 2001</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM118492">section 51(2)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Education Standards Act 2001</amending-leg> (2001 No 88).</history-note>
