            <history-note id="DLM186242"><amended-provision>Section 258(1A)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>inserted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>25 October 2001</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM118494">section 53(1)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Education Standards Act 2001</amending-leg> (2001 No 88).</history-note>
            <history-note id="DLM186244"><amended-provision>Section 258(2)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>25 October 2001</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM118494">section 53(2)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Education Standards Act 2001</amending-leg> (2001 No 88).</history-note>
