            <history-note id="DLM186874"><amended-provision>Section 305(2A)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>inserted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 October 1998</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM429013">section 11</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Employment Services and Income Support (Integrated Administration) Act 1998</amending-leg> (1998 No 96).</history-note>
            <history-note id="DLM186875"><amended-provision>Section 305(3)(c)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 October 1998</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM429013">section 11</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Employment Services and Income Support (Integrated Administration) Act 1998</amending-leg> (1998 No  96).</history-note>
            <history-note id="DLM186876"><amended-provision>Section 305(5)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 October 2003</amendment-date>, pursuant to <amending-provision href="DLM201378">section 14(2)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>State Sector Amendment Act 2003</amending-leg> (2003 No 41).</history-note>
