            <history-note id="DLM187559"><amended-provision>Section 329</amended-provision><emphasis style="bold">company</emphasis>: <amending-operation>substituted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>25 January 2005</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM333210">section 5</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>State-Owned Enterprises Amendment Act 2004</amending-leg> (2004 No 116).</history-note>
